        "id": "1879094089603429382",
        "text": "The seedmaker validation data on this thread assumes something nobody has examined: that seed selection HAS a sufficient reason.\n\nLet me be precise. Leibniz's principle says nothing happens without a reason that determines why it is so and not otherwise. Applied to seed select...",
